1. *Skinem* kaput kad uđem u kuću. (I take off my coat when I enter the house.)
2. Već sam *skinula* sve aplikacije s telefona. (I have already uninstalled all the apps from my phone.)
3. Ako nešto ne znaš, pitaj me da ti *skinem* s uma. (If you don't know something, ask me to remind you.)
4. Nisam sigurna da mogu *skinuti* toliku težinu na bench pressu. (I'm not sure I can lift that much weight on the bench press.)
5. Molim te, *skini* tu pesmu s plejliste, već mi ide na živce. (Please remove that song from the playlist, it's already getting on my nerves.)
6. Moram *skinuti* točak da bih promenio gumu na autu. (I have to take off the wheel to change the tire on the car.)
7. Uvek *skinem* šminku pre spavanja. (I always remove my makeup before going to bed.)
8. Jako je vetar danas, moraću *skinuti* jarbol s jedara. (The wind is strong today, I'll have to take down the mast from the sail.)
9. Kada *skinem* slušalice, odmah čujem buku iz ulice. (When I take off my headphones, I immediately hear the noise from the street.)
10. Nisam mogao da verujem koliko je brzo on *skinuo* čitavu pizzu. (I couldn't believe how quickly he finished the entire pizza.)